Name: Denc, Dik & Cunningham
Review Text: We had a surprise menu from the chef, with 5 course to enjoy; all the plates were well presented and nicely combined. The waiter was very amusing. The restaurant itself is petit and comfortable. We enjoyed it and had a lovely evening!

Name: Denc, Dik & Cunningham
Review Text: The food is wonderful, served in an intimate setting, and the hosts are very generous with extras...not just an amuse-bouche, but several! This is food that can be best compared to a melody -- a range of tastes and ingredients with exquisite presentation that, well, sing. And all for a reasonable price.
